<a name="OutrasInformacoesRelevantes">
<h1>Outras informa&ccedil;&otilde;es relevantes</h1>
</a>
<hr class="separator">
<div class="layout-cell layout-cell-12 data-cell">
<pre class="outras-informacoes">I am a member of the following Associations and Research Groups:
 
1. Work Group (GT)  Ethics of The National Association of Post-Graduation  Anpof (Member and  coordinator).
2. Member of the Research Group  CNPQ Theories of Justice and  Polítical Culture ( Porto Alegre - PUCRS- Brazil)
3. Coordinator of the Research Group on  Ethics and Applied Ethics.
4. Collaborate with the  Center of Ethics and Mind Philosophy of the Federal University of Rio de Janeiro UFRJ-Brazil.
5. Member of the Brazilian Society of Phenomenology.
6. Member of the Brazilian Society of Analitical Philosophy.</pre>
